snippet: Kim English scored 27 points and led a 26-5 first-half run, and No. 5 Missouri swamped Oklahoma State in a quarterfinal game.
abstract: College Basketball Men's Roundup; Missouri defeats Oklahoma State, 88-70, in Big 12 Conference tournament quarterfinals; will face Texas in semifinals; other men's and women's results noted.
lead_paragraph: Kim English scored 27 points and led a 26-5 first-half run, and No. 5 Missouri swamped Oklahoma State in a quarterfinal game.

headline.seo: Missouri Starts Its Final Big 12 Tournament With Rout
headline.main: In Its Big 12 Farewell, Missouri Starts Quickly
headline.print_headline: In Its Big 12 Farewell, Missouri Starts Quickly
